context:
KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;훈훈한 분위기에 초를 치게 되어서 미안하지만…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Apologies for ruining the moment, but…&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그 이후로 몇 년 정도의 시간이 무탈하고, 번잡스럽게 흘러갔지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;The next few years quickly and busily flew by without much trouble.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;몇 번의 최우수 부서 상과, 승진과, 공동 연구 작업도 같이 흘러갔다네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Of course, we picked up ourselves a few more ‘Department of the Year’ awards, some promotions, and some collaborative researches.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그리고 모든 것엔 끝이 있지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Yet all things must come to an end.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;모두가 뻔히 알고 있는 로보토미 코퍼레이션의 끝.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;The infamous fall of Lobotomy Corporation, for one.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그러니까 이 자들이 뭐라고 내게 말을 뱉고 있는지… 들리지 않아도 알 수 있겠지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;So, I don’t suppose you have any trouble hazarding what they're all telling me, even as the words come out fragmented.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;끊임없는 원망의 말뿐.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Nothing but words of endless resentment.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그래, 그렇게 끝난 이야기지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Yes, and that is how this tale ends.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;90초 후 지부는 무너졌고, 나는 부서 직원들을 뒤로 두고 탈출용 엘리베이터를 탑승해 살아남았네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;The compound collapsed ninety seconds later. I left the employees of my department behind and boarded the escape pod elevator, and survived.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;화는 추한 감정일 뿐이야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Wrath is a hideous emotion.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;언제나 냉정하고 이성적으로 살아온 덕에 지금의 자리까지 올 수 있었지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;I am here today only because I have always maintained a cold, rational head.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;자, 이제 뒤틀린 나를 만나러 오게.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Well, now that's over with... I invite you to come face me, the Distortion.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그러면 마침내 실험은 종료야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;And the experiment will come to an end.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;이런 식으로 뒤틀림이 된 저자를 찾아서 물리쳐 봤자…&gt;
EN:
&lt;But… just finding and defeating his Distortion in a fight…&gt;

KR:
&lt;원래대로 돌아오진 않을 거야. 그럴 것 같다는 생각이 들어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... I don’t think that’ll bring him back. I just know it.&gt;
